{"tid":2006919,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"東方日報：多名前警員跟隨上海仔搵食！","createTime":"2020-05-08T05:47:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T09:49:40.000Z","uid":79563,"like":223,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"d0c020d111692f51f5e72df7d32703bb2268b78e","tid":2006919,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T05:47:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/2g83p6aDg3dnN240elMgFQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/2085781854a734eb6b4b5e4caca12c37\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F2g83p6aDg3dnN240elMgFQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F2085781854a734eb6b4b5e4caca12c37&h=b2139a39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7上海仔罪行滔天-涉黃賭毒洗黑錢-214500623.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%25B5%25B7%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E4%BB%94%E7%BD%AA%E8%A1%8C%E6%BB%94%E5%A4%A9-%E6%B6%89%E9%BB%83%E8%B3%AD%E6%AF%92%E6%B4%97%E9%BB%91%E9%8C%A2-214500623.html&d=kJsi%2B77Adq7yP7dZlTZe0LXxB%2B4AiQz8bo105MOPl14%3D&h=77d4105d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7上海仔罪行滔天-涉黃賭毒洗黑錢-214500623.html</a><br />\n<br />\n過往不時出現警黑勾結問題，最受關注的要數在港犯案纍纍的黑幫和勝和前坐館泰國大毒梟「上海仔」郭永鴻，犯案遍及黃賭毒黑及洗黑錢，但至今仍然逍遙法外。他被指與包括助理警務處長在內的多名前高級警務人員關係密切，一直疑獲得警方作保護傘包庇撐腰，犯案更有恃無恐。<br />\n<br />\n上海仔無惡不作，惟過往甚少被拘捕。據知，上海仔與多名前高級警務人員關係密切，職級更高至主力負責打擊販毒、黑社會及洗黑錢的前助理警務處長。而前高級警司王福林退休後更任上海仔「條（口靚）」，跟隨上海仔到澳門搵食。<br />\n<br />\n多名前警員隨上海仔搵食<br />\n<br />\n早在二○一五年十二月，上海仔與王福林涉嫌於澳門盜竊及訛騙，偷取本港富豪存於夾萬的籌碼及現金共六千萬元，其後被該富豪發現，並到澳門報案舉報二人。<br />\n<br />\n澳門當局已正式立案，並循「一般侵犯財產罪」調查，兩人一旦入境澳門，便會立即被扣查，而通緝令至今仍然有效。<br />\n<br />\n另外，多名前警務人員退休後亦跟隨上海仔集團搵食，從事收數等活動。上海仔一八年初嫁女，在尖沙咀五星級酒店設宴筵開約十席，據悉有黑道中人及前高級警務人員出席，更與上海仔同坐在主家席，足證他與不少高級警務人員關係千絲萬縷。<br />\n<br />\n棄保潛逃 流竄歐亞等多國<br />\n<br />\n涉多宗案件的上海仔被捕後棄保潛逃，流竄至泰國、柬埔寨、越南及瑞士，上述國家因與香港仍無引渡協定，故他刻意逃往以迴避追緝。<br />\n<br />\n上海仔主要從事的勾當是一條龍由生產到販賣毒品，毒品主要供應香港、澳門、珠海、深圳、廣州、韓國及日本等地的毒品市場。他因獲警方及律政司兩把保護傘包庇，每次在警方執法前均可聞風先遁。最近，執法部門連番搗破涉及和勝和的毒品案，不排除上海仔「走佬」後，瘋狂出貨。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Fpmx8uQWn36MlUmj0l0oFQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/46ec6a7b8785d65b44719a6b5029fba4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FFpmx8uQWn36MlUmj0l0oFQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F46ec6a7b8785d65b44719a6b5029fba4&h=da9ea77d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王福林（圖）退休後跟隨上海仔到澳門搵食。"},{"pid":"05f5a41e47bddd36fe6d41613950fa38c17f5a83","tid":2006919,"uid":42396,"like":61,"dislike":0,"score":61,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T05:50:19.000Z","msg":"佢個feel有啲似醉爆伴郎團個Peter chu<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf7d01bd64a57c052b0920ea80946a5bdf3a6b97","tid":2006919,"uid":254594,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T11:17:29.000Z","msg":"白粉食錯藥？"},{"pid":"5a90e676cb57f4dfc7fafc731b19ccee22704f30","tid":2006919,"uid":271199,"like":69,"dislike":0,"score":69,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T11:19:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ntiaeuj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNtiaeuj.jpg&h=4da1ea07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kcu1k9m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkcu1k9m.jpg&h=9014e8d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qiXm5A1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqiXm5A1.jpg&h=04dbcc4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UBpTWHH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUBpTWHH.jpg&h=0310ffec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"54adcbd42fa8c1f6fa6b